      "date": "2013-09-03 22:52:13.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Looks good to me, approved\n\nIt would be useful to put in the commit comment how this problem was found.  Was this found by static code analysis to check med_open_lock against med_open_list usage?\n\nIt would also be good to update the comment above mdt_handle2mfd() to indicate that the caller needs to be holding med_open_lock.",
